 Solaris Bank has said its Salary Advance product is aimed at meeting the needs of account and non-account holders, especially during the Yuletide. It explained that the product is a small, short-term unsecured loan that helps the borrower with previous  employment records. It said a beneficiary is expected to repay out of their next month’s pay over time. Polaris Salary Advance, it added, is available, non-collateral facility, and can be accessed anytime, anywhere via *833*12# USSD Smartcode platform. Also, working class persons who are looking for soft credit for their shopping this season, can take advantage and get their account credited within two minutes., the bank added.